      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good starting point, but it's a bit generic. To really tailor the marketing campaign, I need more specifics on the actual demographics. Can you get more granular? I'm thinking about things like age, nationality, ethnicity, and even where they live or where they travel. What's the specific profile of this person?",
