      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The core desire for status remains, but the *expression* of it changes depending on the culture. In some emerging markets, the display of wealth is much more overt and flashy than in the reserved old-money circles. These customers might be more interested in the immediate perceived value and brand recognition than deep historical lineage. However, the fundamental need to signal success and belonging to an elite group is universal, regardless of their background.",
